subject: [ANN] Version 0.2a of Java Gui Builder released !
msgSnippet: Release 0.2a of the Java Gui Builder has been released on SourceForge.net ! This new version adds support for arbitrary method calls. You may download this
messageBody:
Release 0.2a of the Java Gui Builder has been released on SourceForge.net !

This new version adds support for arbitrary method calls.

You may download this release from SourceForge at
http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=50316&release_id=83740

The project's home page is at: http://jgb.sourceforge.net/

Thank you !
Francois Beausoleil
